<title>USA: Topro Inc lowers exercise price of warrants.</title>
<headline>Topro Inc lowers exercise price of warrants.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER, Colo. 1997-05-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Topro Inc said on Friday that it had lowered the exercise price of its publicly held redeemable common stock purchase warrants from $4.25 to $3.50.</p>
<p>The company also said it had extended the expiration date of the warrants to June 24, 1999.</p>
